569
00:30:29,239 --> 00:30:29,680
Here.

570
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:31,599
This is our son.

571
00:30:37,839 --> 00:30:38,959
This is our son.

572
00:30:39,800 --> 00:30:40,880
This is our son.

573
00:30:45,479 --> 00:30:47,479
To be able to hold you
like this right now,

574
