I won't hesitate to do it again

575
00:30:51,439 --> 00:30:52,760
no matter how much I'll suffer.

576
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,719
It's just a liquor bottle.

577
00:31:21,359 --> 00:31:22,719
You've been looking at it for days.

578
00:31:23,599 --> 00:31:25,239
But there's nothing.

579
00:31:28,199 --> 00:31:29,680
What does Ruan Zhimei want?

580
00:31:33,719 --> 00:31:34,800
Madam, look.

581
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:48,359
What is this?

582
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,040
No matter what it is,

583
00:31:55,280 --> 00:31:56,640
I'm sure it's Madam Mei's weakness.

584
00:31:59,199 --> 00:32:00,000
Just now, you said

585
00:32:00,010 --> 00:32:01,230
that you haven't replied to her yet.

586
00:32:01,479 --> 00:32:01,959
Yes.

587
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:05,800
Continue to delay.

588
00:32:07,490 --> 00:32:08,780
Tell her that we didn't have a chance.

589
00:32:09,359 --> 00:32:10,400
Ask her to remain calm.

590
00:32:11,920 --> 00:32:12,280
Yes, Madam.

591
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:16,400
I want to see

592
00:32:17,760 --> 00:32:18,760
how can she remain arrogant

593
00:32:18,760 --> 00:32:19,520
when I have something

594
00:32:20,760 --> 00:32:22,479
that she wants the most.

595
00:32:24,359 --> 00:32:24,800
Madam.

596
00:32:25,599 --> 00:32:26,920
This is delivered to each courtyard.

597
00:32:27,439 --> 00:32:28,160
It's a reward for all

598
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:30,380
in the Young Master's Mansion

599
00:32:30,770 --> 00:32:32,270
to celebrate the birth
of Madam Lian's son.

600
00:32:33,599 --> 00:32:34,880
Let her enjoy this attention for now.

601
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,119
She's the apple

602
00:32:37,119 --> 00:32:38,239
of Young Master's eye now.

603
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,119
But it won't last.

604
00:32:41,239 --> 00:32:42,070
In the end, he still cares

605
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:44,719
about the inheritance more.

606
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:48,920
(Lord Rui's Mansion)

607
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:51,119
Be good, Zhao'er. Stop crying.

608
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:53,839
I've prepared

609
00:32:53,839 --> 00:32:54,920
a lot of rarities for you.

610
00:32:55,119 --> 00:32:56,959
I'll give them all of you

611
00:32:57,439 --> 00:32:58,400
when you are one year old.

612
00:32:59,359 --> 00:33:01,040
Stop crying.

613
00:33:01,280 --> 00:33:02,400
How about I find you

614
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:04,839
a wife who's as beautiful

615
00:33:05,239 --> 00:33:07,280
as your mother

616
00:33:07,479 --> 00:33:08,719
when you grow up?

617
00:33:09,119 --> 00:33:10,280
But I don't think it's possible.

618
00:33:10,520 --> 00:33:11,800
I don't think we can find someone

619
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:12,920
as beautiful as your mother.

620
00:33:13,599 --> 00:33:15,000
Stop crying, Zhao'er.

621
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:16,470
If you are not satisfied with it,

622
00:33:16,760 --> 00:33:17,760
how about I...

623
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:19,959
If you don't feed him now,

624
00:33:20,079 --> 00:33:21,599
he'll only cry harder.

625
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,319
Fine.

626
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:25,479
Here you go.

627
00:33:35,479 --> 00:33:36,000
Look.

628
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:37,599
He loves his nursemaid

629
00:33:37,959 --> 00:33:39,359
more than he loves me.

630
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:42,079
Milk is all he can think about
right now.

631
00:33:42,760 --> 00:33:43,839
But you've fathered

632
00:33:44,280 --> 00:33:45,680
so many children already.

633
00:33:45,839 --> 00:33:46,680
Why does it look like

634
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:47,880
it's your first time?

635
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:49,800
In my heart,

636
00:33:50,719 --> 00:33:51,760
this is my first time.

637
00:33:56,760 --> 00:33:57,119
Here.

638
00:34:01,719 --> 00:34:03,119
Zhao'er is two months old now.

639
00:34:03,520 --> 00:34:04,520
When will I

640
00:34:05,719 --> 00:34:06,760
have another child?

641
00:34:09,959 --> 00:34:11,640
Someone else is about to give birth.

642
00:34:11,959 --> 00:34:12,640
You are going

643
00:34:12,640 --> 00:34:13,639
to be a father again.

644
00:34:15,479 --> 00:34:17,199
You know what I'm talking about.

645
00:34:18,199 --> 00:34:18,639
Here.

646
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:20,919
Young Master.

647
00:34:22,040 --> 00:34:22,560
Young Master.

648
00:34:22,810 --> 00:34:23,930
Madam Zhen has an abdominal pain.

649
00:34:23,940 --> 00:34:24,800
She's about to give birth.

650
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:26,479
I was right.

651
00:34:28,959 --> 00:34:29,760
I'll go and take a look.

652
00:34:30,679 --> 00:34:31,600
I'll go with you.

653
00:34:32,399 --> 00:34:33,560
Stay here

654
00:34:33,660 --> 00:34:34,560
and wait for me to return.

655
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:37,199
Then, finish this bowl
of nourishing porridge.

656
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:39,320
Let's go.

657
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:43,560
(Nan Ruzhen.)

658
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:46,639
(Finally, this day has arrived.)

659
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,399
(Just like you,)

660
00:34:50,679 --> 00:34:51,959
(I've been waiting a long, long time)

661
00:34:52,959 --> 00:34:53,879
(for this.)

662
00:34:57,879 --> 00:34:58,479
Young Master.

663
00:34:58,879 --> 00:35:00,600
Madam Nan is having
a severe abdominal pain.

664
00:35:01,159 --> 00:35:02,280
What did the midwife say?

665
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:04,800
The midwife fainted somehow.

666
00:35:05,719 --> 00:35:06,239
Zhihui.

667
00:35:06,560 --> 00:35:07,840
Go and bring us another midwife.

668
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:08,399
Yes, Madam.

669
00:35:10,399 --> 00:35:11,520
I think it'll be too late.

670
00:35:11,919 --> 00:35:13,000
We can only leave it to God.

671
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:25,600
Lian'er.

672
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:27,320
Young Master.

673
00:35:28,439 --> 00:35:29,159
Why are you here?

674
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:31,239
It's so windy.
Why did you come here?

675
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,679
You can't go in.

676
00:35:39,239 --> 00:35:40,399
Stop me

677
00:35:40,399 --> 00:35:41,399
if you want her dead.

678
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:22,600
Madam.

679
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,170
We have news
from Jingshu Pavilion.

680
00:36:25,479 --> 00:36:26,590
Nan Ruzhen has a difficult labor.

681
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:27,770
And the midwife has fainted.

682
00:36:28,520 --> 00:36:29,120
Looks like

683
00:36:29,679 --> 00:36:30,959
the child won't survive.

684
00:36:32,080 --> 00:36:33,159
Unfortunately, I can't be there

685
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:34,360
because I'm ill.

686
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,080
Otherwise,

687
00:36:36,399 --> 00:36:38,360
with how arrogant

688
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:40,159
she is usually,

689
00:36:41,159 --> 00:36:42,360
I really want to see

690
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:44,120
how she looks right now.

691
00:36:44,919 --> 00:36:45,439
Madam.

692
00:36:47,159 --> 00:36:48,439
I saw Madam Lian

693
00:36:48,439 --> 00:36:50,159
rushing to Jingshu Pavilion just now.

694
00:37:35,479 --> 00:37:36,560
Congratulations, Young Master.

695
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:38,479
Madam Nan has given birth to a boy.

696
00:37:45,919 --> 00:37:46,719
I...

697
00:37:50,639 --> 00:37:51,159
Qinglian.

698
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,840
(Lianwei House)

699
00:38:03,840 --> 00:38:05,919
(Lianwei House)
Young Master didn't even visit Nan Ruzhen.

700
00:38:06,320 --> 00:38:08,159
He stayed here and never left.

701
00:38:08,679 --> 00:38:09,399
Those who don't know

702
00:38:09,679 --> 00:38:11,639
will think that you are the one
who gave birth.

703
00:38:14,159 --> 00:38:14,800
Lian'er.

704
00:38:16,239 --> 00:38:19,040
I never thought that you would do that.

705
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,520
That child has to be born.

706
00:38:23,399 --> 00:38:24,919
And I have to do things that are

707
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:26,570
even more difficult than this.

708
00:38:28,199 --> 00:38:29,399
You say that child.

709
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:30,919
What do you think?

710
00:38:32,199 --> 00:38:33,439
I think our guess

711
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:35,239
is just about right.

712
00:38:37,199 --> 00:38:38,080
That's great.

713
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:42,040
Nan Ruzhen has enjoyed herself
for too long.

714
00:38:43,639 --> 00:38:44,840
It's so long to the point

715
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:46,800
that I thought

716
00:38:47,639 --> 00:38:49,360
I would never be able to take her down.

717
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:52,000
But now,

718
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:54,159
it's different.

719
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:57,760
You.

720
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,919
Bring me a physician right now.

721
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:00,639
You.

722
00:39:00,919 --> 00:39:01,959
Go to the warehouse

723
00:39:02,199 --> 00:39:03,159
to get more coals.

724
00:39:03,479 --> 00:39:04,280
Change her blankets too.

725
00:39:04,479 --> 00:39:05,399
Don't make her catch a cold.

726
00:39:05,959 --> 00:39:07,239
You. Go to the kitchen

727
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:09,380
and ask them to cook and send
something nourishing.

728
00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:10,080
- Yes, Young Master.
- Yes, Young Master.

729
00:39:10,399 --> 00:39:10,959
Yes?

730
00:39:11,560 --> 00:39:12,800
You agreed so readily.

731
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:14,479
Why didn't you stop her

732
00:39:14,879 --> 00:39:16,399
when she did something foolish?

733
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,280
If anything happens to her,

734
00:39:18,399 --> 00:39:19,280
I'll punish all of you.

735
00:39:24,680 --> 00:39:25,770
Why are you still standing here?

736
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:27,040
Go.

737
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,360
- Yes, Young Master.
- Yes, Young Master.

738
