749
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,600
I was just a little bit tired.

750
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:19,439
It was not as serious...

751
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:20,840
- Young Master.
- Young Master.

752
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,239
