to gouge your eyes out?

756
00:40:33,879 --> 00:40:34,840
- No, Young Master.
- No, Young Master.

757
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:40,280
Girl.

758
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,879
I've wronged you.

759
00:40:44,159 --> 00:40:44,919
In the past two years,

760
00:40:45,439 --> 00:40:46,800
Ruzhen had indeed acted

761
00:40:47,080 --> 00:40:48,239
