762
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:49,320
You had suffered a lot

763
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,280
at the secondary courtyard.

764
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:53,170
I thought that you would
harbor hatred toward her.

765
00:40:55,520 --> 00:40:57,280
Looks like I had worried for nothing.

766
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:00,600
Lian'er

767
