00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:36,800
Young Master.

774
00:41:37,239 --> 00:41:38,070
Someone from the Mansion

775
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:38,760
asks you to go there.

776
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:42,380
I'll go to deal with something.

777
00:41:42,679 --> 00:41:44,199
It's cold. Go back and rest earlier.

778
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,320
Keep an eye on her.

779
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:52,239
Take her back earlier
so that she can rest, okay?

780
00:41:52,479 --> 00:41:53,070
Yes, Young Master.

781
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:56,530
- Let's go.
- Farewell, Young Master.

