00:42:23,481 --> 00:42:26,551
♪Only then did I understand
the beauty of the world♪

785
00:42:27,191 --> 00:42:29,581
♪Why, and for what♪

786
00:42:30,531 --> 00:42:33,781
♪Holding pure intentions
in my heart♪

787
00:42:34,151 --> 00:42:36,961
♪Clinging to black and white♪

788
00:42:37,611 --> 00:42:40,441
♪Only then did I realize
that the path is simple♪

789
00:42:41,001 --> 00:42:43,521
♪It is love♪

