00:42:44,391 --> 00:42:45,991
♪When fate♪

791
00:42:46,401 --> 00:42:49,231
♪Surges like deep clouds♪

792
00:42:51,471 --> 00:42:53,241
♪Regardless of♪

793
00:42:53,681 --> 00:42:55,161
